data.description: Charming Renovated End Unit. Full of great features including Hardwood Floors, Recessed Lighting, Plush wall to wall carpet. Gourmet Kitchen with Granite Counter tops, stylish back splash & Stainless Steel Appliances. Off-Street Parking potential. Finished basement  large enough for entertaining with outside entrance. Fenced yard. Half bath on the main level. Spacious dining/kitchen combo. Home features 2 spacious bedrooms and newly renovated bathroom on upper level.   Sellers are motivated. Sellers are offering $4,000 in seller concessions as well.  Sellers will be have carpet professionally cleaned prior to settlement.  The residence is currently occupied so showings must be scheduled and approved.
